📊 Superstore Sales & Profit Dashboard

📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes retail sales data using Excel to generate business insights on sales, profit, customers, and regions.

🛠 Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
XLOOKUP / INDEX-MATCH
Data Cleaning Techniques

📈 Key Insights
Overall profit margin is 11.62%
Technology category is most profitable
Furniture category shows low profitability
West region performs best
Some high-sales customers generate losses
Discounts impact profit negatively

📊 Dashboard Features
KPI Cards (Sales, Profit, Orders, Margin)
Monthly Sales Trend
Sales by Category & Region
Top Customers & Products
Interactive Slicers

